{
  "stem": "21482.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at Oskar Schindler's camp, of course, we had more food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had-- the barracks were small.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was warmer in winter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In summer, when it was very hot, we were allowed to sleep outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember, nights, we just slept outside on blankets because the barracks, you know, we couldn't breathe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no place to escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no way for us to escape because you had to have connection, you have to know people on the outside.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to have money and you had to have the courage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to look Aryan, which we didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I may not-- in United States, it's probably hard to say who looks Aryan and who doesn't.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in Europe, in Poland, Poles knew exactly who was Aryan and who was Jewish, even if the Germans didn't know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, it was dangerous, because if you escaped and the Poles would find you, they would report you to the police and you would be killed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, but there were people who tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were people who tried to hide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were young people who escaped and joined working the Underground in the woods, in the forest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they not only had to hide from the Germans, they had to hide from the Poles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to hide from the Polish Underground because the Polish Underground would hunt the Jewish Underground fighters just like the Germans would.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we just-- we were to-- my mother was alone with a child.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not really a child anymore and I would never think of leaving my mother and doing anything without her, so-- and us, of course, we were still working for Oskar Schindler.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oskar Schindler was-- he was handsome, very handsome, well-dressed.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
